acceleration of North
Korea's movement in a very bad
direction.

11:43.937 --> 11:48.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, what does
this say about
their nuclear capability, where
they can reach,

11:48.841 --> 11:50.710 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
