wreak?

11:50.743 --> 11:54.914 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GREG THIELMANN: It's very hard
to answer that
question precisely, because we
really don't

11:54.948 --> 12:01.654 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
